REPLACE ME.

Reusable line-art SVG icons used inside the app for:
  - Learning module cards (MCQ, Case, OPD, Education)
  - Specialty categories (Cardio, Resp, Neuro …)
  - Achievements + badges

Each icon should be:
  - 24 × 24 viewport
  - single-path where possible
  - currentColor stroke
  - accessible (aria-label attribute in usage)

Naming: kebab-case, purpose-first — e.g. mcq.svg, opd.svg, specialty-cardio.svg.
